blueprint.label: SLS Orbit
blueprint.description:
DO NOT ROTATE!  Though the Space Elevator will move, it will not rotate and thus connections to it will be broken.

Connect red & green wires from elevator the the big power poles on either side.

Set the desired item type for each rocket by putting it with a value of 1 in the associated constant combinator.  Configure the rocket, usally "any destination with the name" and "launch on cargo full".

(optional) Set #1 and #2 fluids is combinators. #3 is reserved for liquid rocket fuel.
